.TH BUILD-ARCHIVE 8
.SH NAME
build-archive \- Build archive of current project and it's requirements, installable locally without internet.
.SH SYNOPSIS
build-archive [-p | --python-executable] [-i | --pip-executable] [-a | --archive-type] [-c | --compression] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Build archive of current project and it's requirements, installable locally without internet.
.SH OPTIONS
-p, --python-executable - Python executable to use for building wheel. Default is python3

-i, --pip-executable - Path to pip executable. Default is pip3.

-a, --archive-type - Type of archive to create. Default is zip, tar is also allowed.

-c, --compression - Type of compression to use. Default is gz. This is only used for tar archive type.

